!! The Larder

[tomtas are here]

[WIP]

Here the autotomtas have set up a little wine-making station (a press that squashes one grape or blackberry at a time). They could put it in a magical tiny jug and cork it, causing it to ferment very quickly. (This was a gift from the grig.) Maybe the wine is fed to the fey to make them drunk. The mice have a secret path to get in here.

Might encounter some ants here.

Can get to the workbench by climbing to the top of the larder, leaping from there to the nearby [[cleansing stone]] next to a basin stand, onto a chair, then onto the workbench.

If tomtas get their motivation back, one of them can make Arien and Dowin invisible, which will help them infiltrate. However once Arien & Dowin get to the desk, the big bad has a [[clockwork faefly]] that can cast [[faerie fire]], making invisible creatures outlined in light.

